g.text: 0x10 | size_t | from // Current offset in buf
0x18 | size_t | count // Bytes remaining in buf

div.p: Unlike raw read_proc, seq_file uses m->index. If userspace reads 10 bytes of a 20-byte line:

ol.li: Next read() returns from m->buf + m->from.
Driver show() is NOT called again until m->count == 0.
